{"tid":941810,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大內揸大膽車 警拉兩教職員","createTime":"2018-12-15T06:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T11:38:01.000Z","uid":20058,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb7f54a1cf000429b28e5408137d83895e59271","tid":941810,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:33:45.000Z","msg":"沙田中文大學有教職員懷疑涉及無牌駕駛。今晨10時11分，保安員在逸夫書院大講堂外，發現一輛豐田私家車左搖右擺，而且左邊車頭損毀凹陷，懷疑司機無牌駕駛，於是致電報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場截停該車，查證司機涉嫌無牌駕駛，隨後找來私家車車主，他涉嫌容許他人無牌駕駛，雙雙被捕。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，兩人均為大學教職員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181215/59032740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181215%2F59032740&d=o2ehRJ8BEYL%2FOkJVW6l0ABv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0217f4ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181215%2F59032740&h=75ff35b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181215/59032740</a>"},{"pid":"d80af69ba376ff84300ef24dfcb4c5f373f5721c","tid":941810,"uid":87339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"冇錢揾師傅練車？"},{"pid":"abbc110978fb2ecb3fb95ae981a2d692083bd3af","tid":941810,"uid":10197,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"晨早流流 中大山鬼影都冇隻<br />\n咪由佢揸到夠囉"},{"pid":"a508d6762e0ee634c5a4477c25590c7ba04b32b2","tid":941810,"uid":16061,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"abbc110978fb2ecb3fb95ae981a2d692083bd3af","tid":941810,"uid":10197,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"晨早流流 中大山鬼影都冇隻<br />\n咪由佢揸到夠囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:43:19.000Z","msg":"個保安咁撚多事 不過佢撞左就真係柒啲"},{"pid":"3c9e0c0231ff66a7c9be28d7460bd26b1ddd45c2","tid":941810,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-1